  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Soap, Scrub, Rinse:Clean Hands for Healthier Kids!</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will support hygiene awareness session for children living in urban deprived communities in the Philippines. The campaign aims to emphasize the importance of hand washing with clean water and soap as the most effective and affordable way to prevent the spread of germs that caused sickness among children.  To enhance their learning and encourage good practices at home, the children will be provided with complete hygiene kits.</narrative>
  </description>
